{"tid":1922882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超官方宣佈本週末聯賽繼續進行","createTime":"2020-03-12T22:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T11:03:32.000Z","uid":173952,"like":24,"dislike":254,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"b35d2b581e46ff8ff53d6ed6e263b5fe55e737a2","tid":1922882,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:18:27.000Z","msg":"香港時間3月13日消息，英超官方發佈公告，本週末聯賽將照常進行。<br />\n<br />\n  英超官方表示，根據英國政府的指示，比賽將繼續進行，同時英國首相表示英國政府在考慮禁止大型公眾活動。<br />\n<br />\n  英超也遭到了新冠疫情的影響，李斯特城教練羅渣士表示隊內有三名球員有疑似新冠的症狀，多支英超球隊也給隊員進行了病毒檢測。"},{"pid":"bdc3ffcfb61d34707e56c91452df8c6505a518db","tid":1922882,"uid":302236,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:28:47.000Z","msg":"阿迪達都中埋招"},{"pid":"4c760f0edb675d3389df9418cda1944b2962e776","tid":1922882,"uid":321837,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:30:44.000Z","msg":"仲有起碼四百病患係街未送院，係唔係搵晒出嚟先搞呢?"},{"pid":"c79102dc36a2e7fa4f5cdddf8120b9e9b368cdfe","tid":1922882,"uid":154649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:31:33.000Z","msg":"阿迪達中左招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93832e1810d909a8af1d533a2a6740bcdb3fe2c2","tid":1922882,"uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:34:41.000Z","msg":"】歐聯出局後，利物浦只餘下英超一條戰線。然而，該隊在聯賽榜遙遙領先少踢一場的曼城二十五分，只要再贏兩仗便能在三月底提早七輪封王，換言之隨時戰至二十二日便提早收咧。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦去年十二月仍可望爭奪四項錦標，但先後於英格蘭聯賽盃和足總盃出局，如今又在歐聯衞冕失敗，只餘下英超冠軍可以爭奪。該隊接下來兩輪聯賽分別作客同市宿敵愛華頓和主場鬥水晶宮，未算太大挑戰，有望再贏兩仗創英超史上最早封王紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n不過，紅軍英超不敗金身早前已被屈福特打破，不敗封王無望，四月開始可能謂無欲無求。難怪隊長佐敦軒達臣提醒隊友道：「我們仍希望踢好每一場，用強勢完成今季。」"},{"pid":"3296b2f29199525da06b57d882218efea36463e5","tid":1922882,"uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvoEKs9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvoEKs9.png&h=c2457b84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"871e2e34de640bbb9dac65474405e65ee970ad4f","tid":1922882,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:35:50.000Z","msg":"聽日會講唔踢架喇"},{"pid":"02f0d8e0ebfe710af06cd34e80606a41fa41db81","tid":1922882,"uid":63936,"like":42,"dislike":6,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:36:11.000Z","msg":"利迷：最好捧埋盃先停"},{"pid":"9fe8afda56bb615718cbfb728003640325c4822b","tid":1922882,"uid":7099,"like":36,"dislike":5,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:36:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母英超班高層<br />\n球員教練都有人奶野 仲係都要踢<br />\n<br />\n100%white trash/利狗"},{"pid":"60f990f45b5c2669839886f6309a1ca4ae2fa2d0","tid":1922882,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:37:00.000Z","msg":"停啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"e3329861c287c03ee0bdf76dd7daa60b6d445026","tid":1922882,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"871e2e34de640bbb9dac65474405e65ee970ad4f","tid":1922882,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:35:50.000Z","msg":"聽日會講唔踢架喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:39:02.000Z","msg":"maybe"},{"pid":"6b52481dd8980f2a73d63d58528e3295a5a3ee7d","tid":1922882,"uid":157828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:39:03.000Z","msg":"停啲屌你老母，教練球員都中，踢條撚？"},{"pid":"ea52f0fcd01ab04ca9469612b4afba374b67d4da","tid":1922882,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:40:14.000Z","msg":"Premier League latest: 'In light of Arsenal&rsquo;s announcement tonight confirming that their first-team coach Mikel Arteta has tested positive for COVID-19, the Premier League will convene an emergency club meeting tomorrow morning regarding future fixtures.'"},{"pid":"997c703e2bba95b4d3dfa6bba18731eb976791e5","tid":1922882,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:41:08.000Z","msg":"3月13日訊 英超通過官方網站發表聲明，本週末的英超比賽將照常進行。 聲明如下：<br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;根據今天下午政府發布的最新消息，所有英超聯賽比賽育將如期在本週末進行。&rdquo;<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n &ldquo;首相先生建議目前所有體育賽事應正常進行</span>，但他還表示，政府正在考慮禁止大型公共聚會，包括體育比賽在內。因此，我們會繼續與我們的俱樂部，政府，足協和其他相關利益攸關 方密切合作，以確保在情況變化時制定適當的應急計劃。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n 球員，員工和球迷們的健康非常重要，我們將繼續嚴格遵守英格蘭公共衛生的指導方針。 我們將視情況繼續向大家提供情況更新。  &rdquo;"},{"pid":"c542f548de40b824cec2b0502d4994355fdc36ea","tid":1922882,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:42:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"6d6d4cb7c0afa270992fb34cf12fe3534a47e075","tid":1922882,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:43:22.000Z","msg":"英超好多賭波外圍係中國人玩，BJ邊敢得罪中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bb672e9d4465e43e3ab9c7bbbd47aac97f090f","tid":1922882,"uid":104423,"like":38,"dislike":11,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"02f0d8e0ebfe710af06cd34e80606a41fa41db81","tid":1922882,"uid":63936,"like":42,"dislike":6,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:36:11.000Z","msg":"利迷：最好捧埋盃先停"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:43:24.000Z","msg":"仲係度打稻草人撩交嗌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8a945ec745e85ca8201f9419f487a14b114608","tid":1922882,"uid":166785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:47:12.000Z","msg":"停了 屌你老母"},{"pid":"f44b2921fb1f7eb43a439760bb6724098f289cad","tid":1922882,"uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:51:53.000Z","msg":"五大聯賽中，已經有意甲、西甲宣布暫停，法甲、德甲空場，英超聯賽本週末正常進行。"},{"pid":"68bc4efae4d887d470bf2868e92bb9c12240f3c9","tid":1922882,"uid":72228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T22:53:30.000Z","msg":"一停d莊仲有咩賭<br />\n梗係要繼續踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nnba停美足又停"},{"pid":"7190de40a1fbad962357db733dae05f6e0eb75da","tid":1922882,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f44b29